        "setup": "Create a guest session by calling the [Create Guest Session](https://developer.themoviedb.org/reference/authentication-create-guest-session) endpoint. TMDB documents guest sessions as limited-permission tokens that can rate movies, TV shows, and TV episodes. Keep the resulting `guest_session_id` private and send it as a query parameter on guest-session endpoints.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      }
